description: This top 5% Gaston purrs with a rating of 86, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 258, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Stringalong for North, 1 for East, 8 for South, and Leverage for West. Gaston has the personality suit of whale. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
